      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/albano-id/{size}/14620_2.png",
      "created_at": "2021-11-25T21:45:17.459Z",
      "cooked": "<p>serite jane nje mpirje truri, arratisje mga realiteti, sikurse videogamet.<br>\nFilmat art dhe essay psrkundrazi kane realitet brenda, kerkojne impenjim. serite e fundit qe kam ndjekur dr house, dhe twin peaks. nese ketij te fundit mund ti rikthehesha, te parit i ka humb kureshtja.<br>\nmeqe ra fjala te taxi driver, kam pare mjaft analiza te atij filmi ne youtube, me i miri per maskulinitetin, ekuivalenti i mulholland drive mbi frustracionin feminil. Per mua disa filma duhen futur ne kurrikulat shkollore, te edukohet fuqia e artit.</p><div class=\"youtube-onebox lazy-video-container\" data-video-id=\"-pAcJ0lFu94\" data-video-title=\"Taxi Driver   A Study of Masculinity &amp; Existentialism\" data-video-start-time=\"\" data-provider-name=\"youtube\">\n  <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-pAcJ0lFu94\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"video-thumbnail\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">\n    <img class=\"youtube-thumbnail\" src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/4/1/41d831bec696e1ae13a73560e315b1190bd58d38.jpeg\" title=\"Taxi Driver   A Study of Masculinity &amp; Existentialism\" data-dominant-color=\"575757\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\">\n  </a>\n</div>\n",
      "reply_to_post_number": null,
